      <p style="margin:0 0 24px;">
        A <strong style="color:#e9d5ff;">tip calculator</strong> is a free online tool that instantly computes how much gratuity to leave based on your bill amount and the level of service you received. Whether you're dining at a restaurant, visiting a nail salon, getting a haircut, or ordering from DoorDash, knowing exactly <strong style="color:#e9d5ff;">how much to tip</strong> saves you from awkward mental math at the table. Real Tip Calculator is the most complete, simple tip calculator available — no app download, no account, no fees. Just open it on any device, including your iPhone or Android, and get instant results.
      </p>

      <h3 style="font-family:'Manrope',sans-serif; font-size:22px; font-weight:700; color:#ffffff; margin:0 0 12px;">
        How to Use This Online Tip Calculator
