      <p style="margin:0 0 16px;">
        Using our <strong style="color:#e9d5ff;">free tip calculator</strong> is as easy as three steps:
      </p>
      <ol style="margin:0 0 24px; padding-left:20px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:10px;">
        <li><strong style="color:#e9d5ff;">Enter your bill amount</strong> — type the pre-tax or post-tax total. You can select your currency (USD, EUR, GBP, INR, and more).</li>
        <li><strong style="color:#e9d5ff;">Rate the service quality</strong> — drag the slider from Poor to Excellent. The tool auto-suggests the standard tip percentage based on your rating, so you never under-tip or over-tip.</li>
        <li><strong style="color:#e9d5ff;">Split the bill</strong> — enter the number of people to instantly see the per-person cost including their share of the tip.</li>
      </ol>
      <p style="margin:0 0 24px;">
        The results update in real time. You'll see the tip amount, the total bill, and the per-person breakdown — all calculated using the standard <strong style="color:#e9d5ff;">tip calculator formula</strong>: <em>Tip = Bill × (Tip% ÷ 100)</em>. You can also enter a custom tip percentage, apply a round-up suggestion for a cleaner total, and copy the full breakdown to share with your group.
      </p>

      <h3 style="font-family:'Manrope',sans-serif; font-size:22px; font-weight:700; color:#ffffff; margin:0 0 12px;">
